      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="*This design could be subject to change based on specific country requirements/ feedback received from interlock teams and can be reviewed holistically in R3S8 for changes needed.&#10;&#10;The Manage Withholding Tax Determination - Vendor Data is a process to track how much tax should be withheld from suppliers based on different countries' tax policies. Withholding tax certificates should be provided as supporting documents to suppliers. BRF+ in SAP is being used to help calculate the withholding amount."/>
